c: 6
v: 139
t: "Futhi bathi “Lokho okuseziswini zalezizinkomo kungokwabesilisa bethu kuphela futhi kwenqatshelwe kwabesifazane bethu, kepha uma kuzalwe kufile ngakho-ke bona bayohlanganyela kukona uyobanika umvuzo (isijeziso) ngencazelo\tyabo\t(engesilona\tiqiniso)\tngempela\tyena unobuhlakani uyazi”"